  npcName: Skull
  npcSprite: {fileID: 3737911869956679271, guid: f190aa02b185e014fa8686686bfcd3be, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Welcome, Michael... to Mobius.
  - This is the temple of your mind.
  - Would you perhaps need anything?
  - Of course.
  - Morbius is the labyrinth you created, Michael.
  - You have lost yourself, young one.
  - You must face what is ahead in this dungeon to truly reconcile with yourself.
  - And you must do so... at any cost.
